headline: The Smartest Dividend Stocks to Buy With $3,000 Right Now
summary: As the stock market has moved higher, one victim has been dividend yields.  With the average payout for the S&P 500 down to just 1.25%, such stocks have lost a bit of appeal at a time when investors can earn a guaranteed return of around 5% in some certificates of deposit.  Admittedly, AT&T's (NYSE: T) recent dividend history may make its stock a strange choice at first glance.

headline: Largest U.S. Pension Sold GE Aerospace and Tesla Stock, Bought AT&T and Costco
summary: Calpers sold GE Aerospace and Tesla stock, and bought more shares of AT&T and Costco in the third quarter.
